<span id="freeTextContainer12328183042833699633">This read like a really bad fanfiction. The only reason it gets more than one star is because it shows a lot of character diversity. <br/><br/>Marisol is such an annoying character. Even more annoying that Olivia. Olivia is awful and cruel. But she’s less annoying than somebody like Marisol who not once showed any redeemable qualities.</span>

